product.name: Group Life GBP
product.entityDescription: Within a GBP contract, only coverage from one GBP Model can be chosen, and it is not possible to customize rules.

options.name: Employee Term Life
options.entityDescription: Basic Group Term Life coverage provides a basic level of life insurance, often paid for by the employer.

options.name: Spouse Term Life
options.entityDescription: Basic Group Term Life coverage provides a basic level of life insurance, often paid for by the employer.

options.name: Employee Accidental Death & Dismemberment
options.entityDescription:
Accidental Death and Dismemberment (AD&D) provides funds in the event of a fatal accident for an accident that results in the loss of a limb or eyesight.

This benefit is paid out as an annuity. A lump sum amount can also be paid out to cover Funeral cost.
